{"Id":477,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-anonymousgroupo","Author":"Anonymous Group Of Translators","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"Goodword Books , http://www.goodwordbooks.com/ , Center for Peace and Spirituality , https://www.cpsglobal.org/","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"你当赞颂你至尊主的大名超绝万物，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"他创造万物， 并使各物匀称。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他预定万物，而加以引导。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"他生出牧 草，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"然后使它变成黑色的枯草。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"我将使你诵读，故你 不会忘记，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"除非真主所欲你忘记的。他的确知道显著的 和隐微的言行。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"我将使你遵循平易的道路，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"故你当教 诲众人，如果教诲有裨于他们的话。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"畏主的人，将觉 悟"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"薄命的人，将退避，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"他将入于大火，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"然后， 在火里不死也不活。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"有教养的人确已成功，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"他记念 他的主的尊名，而谨守拜功。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"不然，你们却选择今世的 生活；"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"其实，后世是更好的，是更久长的。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"这确是 载在古经典中的，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"载在易卜拉欣和穆萨的经典中的。"}]}